snippet: The prosecutor overseeing the investigation of sexual-assault allegations against Florida State quarterback Jameis Winston said it was complete.
abstract: Prosecutor overseeing investigation into sexual-assault allegations against Florida State quarterback Jameis Winston announces it is complete and that findings will soon be released.
lead_paragraph: The prosecutor overseeing the investigation of sexual-assault allegations against Florida State quarterback Jameis Winston said it was complete.

headline.main: Prosecutor Completes Investigation of F.S.U. Quarterback
